.astro/

# secrets — OAuth.md (root) keeps Google client_id + client_secret in
# plaintext for local dev convenience. NEVER commit it: rotating the secret
# in the GCP console is the only sane response if it leaks.
# (api/.env* patterns are covered by api/.gitignore to keep concerns local.)
OAuth.md

